@startuml t_sequence_03_lifeline_control
title Sequence Diagram — Lifeline Control\n(activate, deactivate, destroy, return, autoactivate, nested, colored)

participant "Client"      as CLI
participant "API Gateway" as GW
participant "Auth Service" as AUTH
participant "Order Service" as ORDSVC
participant "Inventory"   as INV
participant "Payment"     as PAY
participant "Notifier"    as NOTIF
participant "Logger"      as LOG

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 1. BASIC ACTIVATE / DEACTIVATE
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== Basic activate / deactivate ==

CLI -> GW : GET /orders
activate GW
GW --> CLI : 200 OK
deactivate GW

CLI -> GW : POST /orders
activate GW
GW -> AUTH : validateToken()
activate AUTH
AUTH --> GW : token valid
deactivate AUTH
GW --> CLI : order created
deactivate GW

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 2. ACTIVATE WITH COLOR  activate ALIAS #color
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== activate with color ==

CLI -> GW : POST /orders (colored lifelines)
activate GW #FFE0B2
GW -> AUTH : validateToken()
activate AUTH #E3F2FD
AUTH -> LOG : logAccess()
activate LOG #E8F5E9
LOG --> AUTH : logged
deactivate LOG
AUTH --> GW : valid
deactivate AUTH
GW -> ORDSVC : createOrder()
activate ORDSVC #FCE4EC
ORDSVC --> GW : orderId=42
deactivate ORDSVC
GW --> CLI : 201 Created
deactivate GW

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 3. NESTED ACTIVATIONS (stacked lifeline bars)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== Nested activations ==

CLI -> GW : complexRequest()
activate GW

GW -> ORDSVC : processOrder()
activate ORDSVC

ORDSVC -> INV : checkStock()
activate INV
INV -> LOG : logCheck()
activate LOG
LOG --> INV : logged
deactivate LOG
INV --> ORDSVC : stock available
deactivate INV

ORDSVC -> PAY : chargePayment()
activate PAY
PAY -> LOG : logPayment()
activate LOG
LOG --> PAY : logged
deactivate LOG
PAY --> ORDSVC : charged
deactivate PAY

ORDSVC -> NOTIF : sendConfirmation()
activate NOTIF
NOTIF --> ORDSVC : queued
deactivate NOTIF

ORDSVC --> GW : order complete
deactivate ORDSVC

GW --> CLI : 200 OK
deactivate GW

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 4. RETURN KEYWORD  (deactivates + sends return message)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== return keyword ==

CLI -> GW : getUser(id)
activate GW
GW -> AUTH : authenticate()
activate AUTH
AUTH -> LOG : log()
activate LOG
return logged
AUTH --> GW : authenticated
deactivate AUTH
return user data

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 5. DESTROY KEYWORD  (lifeline ends with X)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== destroy keyword ==

CLI -> GW : deleteSession()
activate GW
GW -> AUTH : invalidateToken()
activate AUTH
AUTH --> GW : token invalidated
destroy AUTH
GW --> CLI : session deleted
deactivate GW

CLI -> ORDSVC : cancelOrder(42)
activate ORDSVC
ORDSVC -> PAY : refundPayment()
activate PAY
PAY --> ORDSVC : refunded
deactivate PAY
ORDSVC -> INV : restoreStock()
activate INV
INV --> ORDSVC : stock restored
deactivate INV
ORDSVC --> CLI : order cancelled
destroy ORDSVC

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 6. AUTOACTIVATE ON / OFF
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== autoactivate on ==

autoactivate on

CLI -> GW : autoRequest()
GW -> AUTH : autoValidate()
AUTH --> GW : autoValid
GW --> CLI : autoResponse

autoactivate off

== autoactivate off (back to manual) ==

CLI -> GW : manualRequest()
activate GW
GW --> CLI : manualResponse
deactivate GW

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 7. ACTIVATE + RETURN IN SAME BLOCK (shorthand pattern)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== activate + return shorthand ==

CLI -> GW : shorthandFlow()
activate GW #LightBlue

GW -> ORDSVC : step1()
activate ORDSVC #LightGreen
ORDSVC -> INV : step1a()
activate INV #LightYellow
return inResult
return step1Result

GW -> PAY : step2()
activate PAY #LightPink
return step2Result

return finalResponse

' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
' 8. MULTIPLE ACTIVATIONS OF SAME PARTICIPANT (stacking)
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

== Multiple activations (stack) ==

CLI -> GW : outer()
activate GW
CLI -> GW : inner() [recursive]
activate GW #FF8888
GW --> CLI : inner result
deactivate GW
GW --> CLI : outer result
deactivate GW

note right of GW
    **Grammar targets (lifeline):**
    activate ALIAS
    activate ALIAS #color
    deactivate ALIAS
    destroy ALIAS
    return [label]
    autoactivate on
    autoactivate off
    Nested activate (stack bars)
    Multiple activate same participant
end note

note right of AUTH
    **return keyword:**
    Sends a return arrow AND
    deactivates the current
    activation frame.
    Equivalent to:
      --> caller : label
      deactivate self
end note

@enduml
